      "title": "Biases in Dynamic Models with Fixed Effects",
      "abstract": "Abstract This paper examines bias in dynamic models with fixed effects where both the number of time series observations and the number of cross-sectional replications are small. The formula bias estimate is in line with that in published Monte Carlo studies."
